           move      spaces               to   w-tes-cod-prv-des (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-cod-prv-cmi (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-cod-prv-cma (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-cod-prv-cpl (1)  .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-cod-prv-ist (1)  .
           go to     acc-cod-prv-058.
